text: Karel Koldovský (10 June 1898 - 29 April 1943) was a Czech ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1924 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1898 births Category:1943 deaths Category:Czech male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Czechoslovakia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1924 Winter Olympics Category:People from Vysoké nad Jizerou
